From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Buildroot <buildroot@buildroot.org>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 13:11:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] package/giflib: bump to version 6.1.2

Fixes download failure of giflib-5.2.2.tar.gz which is no longer
available on SourceForge.

https://sourceforge.net/p/giflib/code/ci/6.1.2/tree/NEWS

Signed-off-by: Bernd Kuhls <bernd.kuhls@t-online.de>
